<P>BY WILLIAM SCOTT, TEACHER OF ENGLISH READING, AND AUTHOR OF A <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> SPELLING AND PRONOUNCING DICTIONARY, &amp;c.</P>
